#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:53
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:53
msgid "Find the file you downloaded.  Right click it, and choose \"Extract All…\""
msgstr "Trouvez le fichier que vous avez téléchargé. Faites un clic droit dessus et choisissez \"Extract all…\""

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:62
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:62
msgid "Click \"Extract\""
msgstr "Cliquez sur \"Extract\""

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:71
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:71
msgid "Find the extracted files.  Optionally, right click \"openrefine\" and choose \"Send to → Desktop (create shortcut)\" to create a shortcut on your desktop.  Then double click \"openrefine\""
msgstr "Trouvez les fichiers extraits. En option, faites un clic droit sur « openrefine» et choisissez « \"Send to → Desktop (create shortcut)» pour créer un raccourci sur votre bureau. Puis double-cliquez sur \"openrefine\""

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:80
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:80
msgid "A black console window opens, and a short time later the browser opens.  OpenRefine is now ready to use."
msgstr "Une fenêtre de console noire s'ouvre, et peu de temps plus tard le navigateur s'ouvre. OpenRefine est maintenant prêt à l'emploi."

#. type: Title ==
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:83
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:83
#, no-wrap
msgid "Installation on Mac"
msgstr "Installation sur Mac"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:88
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:88
msgid "Download, open, drag icon into the Applications folder.  You do not need to install Java separately."
msgstr "Téléchargez, ouvrez, glissez l'icône dans le dossier d'applications. Vous n'avez pas besoin d'installer Java séparément."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:89
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:89
msgid "Double click on it and a new web browser window will show the application."
msgstr "Faites un double clic dessus et une nouvelle fenêtre de navigateur Web affichera l'application."

#. type: Block title
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:90
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:90
#, no-wrap
msgid "Detailed instructions for Mac (click to expand)"
msgstr "Instructions détaillées pour Mac (cliquez pour développer)"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:109
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:109
msgid "A warning is shown. Click \"OK\"."
msgstr "Un avertissement est affiché. Cliquez sur \"OK\"."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:118
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:118
msgid "Open System Preferences."
msgstr "Ouvrir les Préférences Système."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:127
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:127
msgid "Open Security & Privacy"
msgstr "Ouvrir Sécurité et confidentialité"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:136
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:136
msgid "Choose \"Open Anyway\" at the bottom."
msgstr "Choisissez \"Open Anyway\" en bas de page."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:145
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:145
msgid "Choose \"Open\""
msgstr "Choisissez \"Open\""

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:154
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:154
msgid "Finally, the application archive is opened! Drag it to your Applications folder."
msgstr "Enfin, l'archive de l'application est ouverte ! Glissez-la dans votre dossier Applications."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:163
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:163
msgid "Double-click the OpenRefine icon.  Another security warning appears!"
msgstr "Double-cliquez sur l'icône OpenRefind. Une autre alerte de sécurité s'affiche !"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:172
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:172
msgid "Go back to \"Security & Privacy\" and click \"Open Anyway\" — again."
msgstr "Retournez à \"Security & Privacy\" et cliquez sur \"Open Anyway\" — à nouveau."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:181
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:181
msgid "(To avoid these warnings, the OpenRefine developers would need to pay Apple.)"
msgstr "(Pour éviter ces avertissements, les développeurs d'OpenRefine devaient payer Apple.)"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:183
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:183
msgid "Click \"Open\"."
msgstr "Cliquez sur \"Open\"."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:192
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:192
msgid "Finally! The application is running."
msgstr "Enfin ! L'application est en cours d'exécution."

#. type: Title ==
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:196
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:196
#, no-wrap
msgid "Installation on Linux"
msgstr "Installation sur Linux"

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:201
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:201
msgid "Download, extract, then type ./refine to start.  This requires Java to be installed on your computer."
msgstr "Téléchargez, extrayez, puis tapez ./refine pour démarrer. Cela nécessite que Java soit installé sur votre ordinateur."

#. type: Block title
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:202
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:202
#, no-wrap
msgid "Detailed instructions for Linux (click to expand)"
msgstr "Instructions détaillées pour Linux (cliquez pour développer)"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:206
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:206
msgid "These instructions are for KDE (e.g. Kubuntu, SuSE), but the process is similar for Gnome (e.g. Ubuntu, Red Hat, CentOS)."
msgstr "Ces instructions sont pour KDE (par exemple, Kubuntu, SuSE), mais le processus est similaire pour Gnome (par exemple, Ubuntu, Red Hat, CentOS)."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:223
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:223
msgid "Click \"Extract\" to unpack the downloaded application."
msgstr "Cliquez sur « Extract » pour décompresser l'application téléchargée."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:232
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:232
msgid "Choose a suitable place.  I also selected \"Open destination folder after extraction\" and \"Close Ark after extraction\""
msgstr "Choisissez un endroit approprié. Sélectionnez aussi \"Open destination folder after extraction\" et \"Close Ark after extraction\""

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:241
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:241
msgid "Right click \"refine\" and choose \"Run in Konsole\".  This is needed so you can safely exit OpenRefine later, by closing the Konsole window."
msgstr "Faites un clic droit sur « refine» et choisissez « Run in Konsole», ce qui est nécessaire pour que vous puissiez quitter en toute sécurité OpenRefine plus tard, en fermant la fenêtre Konsole."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:250
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:250
msgid "Confirm that you wish to execute the downloaded application."
msgstr "Confirmez que vous souhaitez exécuter l'application téléchargée."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:259
#: en/foundations/modules/ROOT/pages/install-openrefine.adoc:259
msgid "OpenRefine is now running."
msgstr "OpenRefine est en cours d'exécution."

